# TLC model-checker scratch files (mirrors ~/src/graphrefly/formal/.gitignore).
# `states/` holds per-worker BFS state snapshots + fingerprint files,
# regenerated on every TLC run. `MC.out`, the tooling-generated `MC.tla`,
# and `MC.cfg` are TLC's internal harness copies (NOT our authored
# `*_MC.tla` / `*_MC.cfg` source files — those are tracked).
docs/research/states/
docs/research/*.toolbox/
docs/research/MC.out
